code: /**  * Resolve the given {@code Supplier}, getting its result or immediately  * returning {@code null} if the supplier itself was {@code null}.  * @param supplier the supplier to resolve  * @return the supplier's result, or {@code null} if none  */ @Nullable public static <T> T resolve(@Nullable Supplier<T> supplier) {     return (supplier != null ? supplier.get() : null). }
